
welcome to create-node-mrc utility tool
This utility tool helps to initialize a node express api.

What do you want to do?
[] Initialize new node express app (MRC) (1)
[] Create a resource (2)
[] Exit


Case 1:
    What is the name of your project? :___________
    Select the directory of your projecet :(leave blank to use the current folder, supply a full directory Path):___________
    Select addtional dependencies to add to your project, Core dependencies are (mongoose,)
        [] jsonwebtoken
        [] bcrypt


Case 2:
    What is the name of the resource :___________
    Select additional files to be created
        () Modal (for db management)
        () Routes (for api linking)
        () Utility (for utility tools)
    
Case 3:
    Good bye